这是你的丈夫

507
00:39:38,120 --> 00:39:39,120
Your daughter?
你的女儿

508
00:39:53,930 --> 00:39:55,890
You went in the book when l came out.
当我出来的时候  你被吸进了书里

509
00:39:57,970 --> 00:39:59,390
You went in the book...
你进入了书里

510
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:01,430
...when l came out...
当我出来的时候

511
00:40:02,690 --> 00:40:04,980
...and then Darius read you out again.
然后达利尔斯又把你读出来

512
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:06,560
Gwin.
葛文

513
00:40:11,990 --> 00:40:15,660
l'm gonna get you out of these chains, and then you're going home.
我要把这些铁链弄断 你就可以回家了

514
00:40:28,210 --> 00:40:30,260
l'll meet you at the stables.
在马房见

515
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:19,050
l've never been that in control before.
我以前从未感受过这种力量

516
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:22,890
l know l can get Resa out of the book.
我知道我能把瑞莎救出来

517
00:41:23,430 --> 00:41:25,730
And maybe send Capricorn back in.
然后把摩羯赶回到书里

518
00:41:26,060 --> 00:41:27,690
We just have to find another copy.
但我们必须找到另一本书

519
00:41:27,860 --> 00:41:30,690
Well, it only took you nine years to find the last one.
是啊  找到上一本也不过就花了9年时间嘛

520
00:41:32,230 --> 00:41:33,820
l bet the author has a copy.
作者肯定有一本

521
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:38,240
lf he's alive, l bet he'd have one.
如果他还活着  肯定有原著

522
00:41:38,410 --> 00:41:40,620
Someone must know where he lives.
一定有人知道他在哪里

523
00:41:40,780 --> 00:41:44,410
Great. Now we're going to have to try to escape, aren't we?
棒极了  现在我们要越狱了  是吗

524
00:41:44,750 --> 00:41:47,580
